_Ethernet Fundamentals_						 

1 Ethernet dominant leadre in market 

1 deterministic # когда кто-то поднял руку на уроке чтобы спросить 
2 Contention based  # у каждого своя очередь разговора
ethernet using contention based 

Carrier Sense Multiple Access /Collision Detect (CSMA/CD)
Ethernet devices transmit based on a principle called carrirer sense multiple access/collision detec (CSMA/CD)

Ethernet слушает если никто не говорит по кабелю тогда он начинает говорить 
If I go left and he goes left I will stop and wait when will go, then I will start.

1 2 3
4 5 6 
3  want to communicate with 5 in the same time. wil work backoff 3 120 ms(возврат) and 5 30 ms(возврат), then 5 will start to talk after it 3 wil strat to talk  its liki walkie talkie

Collision Domains with Switches  (bits per second (1 second) )
1 ethernet 10 mbps  10 million bits per second

2 Fast ethernet  100 mbps  100 million bits per second

3 gigabit ehernet 1000 mbps (1 gps) 1 billion bits per second (1 0 can network transmit in network)

4 10-Gigabit Ethernet  10 Gbps 10 billion bits per second 
5 100 gigabit ethernet 100 gbps  100 billion bits per second 
