3 Orthogonal frequency-division multiplexing (OFDM)     !!!!!



1  direct-sequence spread spectrum (DSSS)
siries of signals known as chips 
802.11b (DSSS) channel width 22 mhz # very popelar in 2,4 ghz 


2 frequency-hopping spread spectrum (FHSS)
better if you need eveything more secure

3 Frequencies and Channels 
Частоты и каналы
IEEE 802.11 two standards:
1. 2,4 ghz band 

2. 5 ghz band 5,75 ghz to 5,875 ghz range 
диапазон ГГЦ (band) имеет свои частоты для избежения перекрытия сигналов

!!!!!
standard 		band(ghz) 		maximum Bandwidth             transmission       maximum range
				 диапозон ГГЦ    пропускная способность			method          in=inddors out=outdoors

1 802.11 			2.4 gnz  	1 mbps of 2 mbps   				dsss or fhss       20m in 100m out !!!

2 802.11a            5 ghz 	 		54mbps 							ofdm           35m in 120m out

3 802.11b 			2,4 ghz 		11 mbps 						DSSS           32m in 140m out

4 802.11g             2,4 ghz 	     54 mbps                        ofdm or dsss   32m in 140m out

5 802.11n			2,4 5, both      300 mbps                         ofdm          70m in 250m out !!!
									channel banding 
6 802.11ac				5 			3gbps 							ofdm            70m in 250m out  !!! very fast



4 radio frequency interference (RFI)
1 other wi-fi devices 
2 cordless phones and baby monitors (2.4 ghz)
3 microwave ovens (2.4 ghz)
